1. Data Collection:
1.1 No Data Collection:
Our company maintains a strict policy of not collecting any personal or sensitive information from users. This includes, but is not limited to, personal names, addresses, phone numbers, financial information, or browsing history. We do not collect or store any user data of any kind.
 
1.2 Device Data:
We do not collect any information related to your device, including Device ID, location, or other identifiers. No data is transmitted or stored from your device.
 
1.3 App Permissions:
Our application does not require any permissions to access device functionalities such as contacts, location, storage, or camera.
 
2. Data Usage:
We do not use any data for any purpose as we do not collect or store any information from users.
 
3. Data Sharing and Transfer:
Since we do not collect any data, there is no data to share or transfer to any third parties. Your privacy is fully protected.
 
4. Security Measures:
As we do not store or process any user data, no security measures are required for protecting any personal information.
 
5. Data Retention:
We do not retain any user data. As no data is collected, there is nothing to retain or delete.
 
6. Advertising:
Our App uses Google Admob to display advertisements. Admob may collect certain information about your device and your activity within the App, such as your device ID, advertising IDand location. Admob may use this information to serve you personalized ads.
7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy:
It is recommended that parents educate their children about online privacy and data protection. Our app does not collect or store any information from children.
 
